I just remembered

03:42.464 --> 03:44.732
I promised my best friend
Julie we'd hang out.

03:44.816 --> 03:48.052
Unless you could
bring a friend for her.

03:48.120 --> 03:50.121
Oh! Oh-oh,
yeah. No prob!

03:50.188 --> 03:52.573
Great. Oh, and just
so you know,

03:52.641 --> 03:54.442
I end up going
all the way

03:54.509 --> 03:56.077
on the first date
every time.

03:56.144 --> 03:57.345
Is that okay?

03:57.412 --> 03:58.713
With me, it is.

03:58.780 --> 04:00.548
I would not tell
anyone else that.

04:00.616 --> 04:02.850
