on this repair order.

04:14.313 --> 04:17.048
I didn't think the demand for 17th
century ironwork was this brisk.

04:17.115 --> 04:18.716
When did you
learn how to weld?

04:18.784 --> 04:20.334
This morning. Didn't
even read the manual.

04:20.402 --> 04:21.535
Just dove right in.

04:21.603 --> 04:22.970
