05:22.397 --> 05:24.165
in the industry before.

05:24.232 --> 05:26.000
Mr. Smith, I'm sorry,

05:26.068 --> 05:28.002
but I don't think
I can approve this loan.

05:28.070 --> 05:29.820
But, sir, please!

05:29.888 --> 05:31.188
