05:31.256 --> 05:33.791
Do some of the confi-dance.

05:33.842 --> 05:36.861
Okay, listen to me and everybody
lives a lot longer!

05:36.928 --> 05:38.045
Oh, my God!

05:38.113 --> 05:39.480
