to eat good food.

05:46.238 --> 05:48.005
Not canned and frozen foods,

05:48.073 --> 05:50.775
not foods trucked in
from out of state.

05:50.826 --> 05:52.009
No!

05:52.077 --> 05:53.944
Who believes food
should be grown locally

05:54.012 --> 05:55.046
with no pesticides?

05:55.113 --> 05:56.180
Farm to table.

05:56.248 --> 05:57.882
Plate to face.

05:57.949 --> 06:00.551
Because that's the kind of
restaurant my friend is opening.

06:00.619 --> 06:02.019
Who wants to eat
at his restaurant?

06:02.087 --> 06:03.187
