Great.

06:03.255 --> 06:04.588
I'd love that.
Plate to face.

06:04.656 --> 06:07.792
Best presentation ever.

06:07.843 --> 06:09.794
Looks like you're in business.

06:09.845 --> 06:12.279
Good morning!

06:12.347 --> 06:15.082
