06:37.023 --> 06:39.424
Stan, that was the phone call
we've been waiting for.

06:39.492 --> 06:40.559
We got Qui-Lo,

06:40.626 --> 06:42.994
the Laotian midget master chef.

06:43.062 --> 06:47.299
Oh, well, I was kind of thinking
we'd keep things simple and fun.

06:47.366 --> 06:49.334
See, I made up
a sample menu.

06:49.402 --> 06:51.703
Wow, what's, what's
a ravioli burger?

06:51.771 --> 06:53.705
It's a hamburger
with all the trimmings

06:53.773 --> 06:55.941
