little potsticker?

07:04.350 --> 07:06.017
He could cook this
stuff in his sleep.

07:06.085 --> 07:07.352
Are you sure?

07:07.420 --> 07:09.221
Trust me. I know
the restaurant business.

07:09.288 --> 07:12.257
I managed a Hardee's
in Myrtle Beach for three years.

07:12.325 --> 07:14.526
Everyone called it
"Party Hardee's" 'cause

07:14.594 --> 07:16.895
