it might be brown on the inside?

08:43.115 --> 08:44.516
Like a powdered
chocolate donut.

08:44.584 --> 08:46.535
Mmm... Now you're
making me hungry.

08:46.602 --> 08:47.736
How's my dream coming?

08:47.803 --> 08:48.920
I've been running
around so much,

08:48.988 --> 08:50.572
I haven't had
a chance to see...

08:50.640 --> 08:51.706
