my scale model?

11:35.621 --> 11:37.422
Stan, it took quite
a bit of doing,

11:37.490 --> 11:39.591
but I managed to wipe
my butt with it.

11:39.658 --> 11:40.725
What?
Look, it's time

11:40.793 --> 11:41.910
for some opening-
night honesty.

11:41.977 --> 11:43.278
Your ideas
are terrible.

11:43.346 --> 11:44.379
I've done you a favor.

11:45.481 --> 11:46.414
Qui-Lo, shut up!

11:46.482 --> 11:48.083
