11:58.377 --> 11:59.377
Where's the ravioli burger?

11:59.445 --> 12:00.912
Where is it?

12:00.980 --> 12:02.947
It's in your head
where it belongs.

12:03.015 --> 12:04.616
Because it's stupid.

12:04.683 --> 12:06.985
It's in your
stupid head.

12:07.053 --> 12:08.536
You son of a bitch!

12:08.604 --> 12:09.637
You insult my mother?!

12:09.705 --> 12:11.673
If you had half
the culinary talent

12:11.741 --> 12:12.991
she had in her
little finger...!

12:14.009 --> 12:15.143
What?!

12:15.211 --> 12:16.778
Oh, my God!

12:20.049 --> 12:22.200
Oh! Oh!

12:22.268 --> 12:23.901
It's a girl!
Oh!

12:26.205 --> 12:27.939
She's so beautiful!

12:29.408 --> 12:31.426
Oh, look at that!

12:31.510 --> 12:32.927
Would you look
at that!

12:55.851 --> 12:57.819
...in my mother's
little finger

12:57.887 --> 12:59.621
than you have in
your entire body,

12:59.688 --> 13:00.789
you no-talent hack!

13:00.856 --> 13:02.390
You know what?
You're fired!

13:02.458 --> 13:04.426
You can't fire me
from my own restaurant!

13:04.493 --> 13:06.027
Actually,
it's all mine.

13:06.095 --> 13:08.029
The bank wouldn't
lend you 50 cents!

13:08.097 --> 13:10.231
The restaurant, the truck,
the napkin holders,

13:10.299 --> 13:11.332
they're all mine!

13:11.400 --> 13:13.234
But to show you
I'm a good guy,

13:13.302 --> 13:15.804
I got you this. Ta-dah!

13:15.871 --> 13:16.888
The perfect split.

13:16.956 --> 13:17.922
You like that?

13:17.990 --> 13:19.190
Get off my property.

13:24.716 --> 13:26.951
I can't believe
Roger fired you!

13:27.018 --> 13:29.453
He told me all my
ideas were stupid.

13:29.521 --> 13:31.255
You can't let him steal
your dream.

13:31.323 --> 13:32.389
It's too late, Francine.

13:32.457 --> 13:33.924
It's already done.

13:33.992 --> 13:36.227
I'm gonna grab
some shut-eye.

13:36.311 --> 13:38.646
Maybe dream a new dream!

13:41.733 --> 13:43.217
Francine, we've
been driving for hours.

13:43.268 --> 13:45.319
Are we at
the frozen yogurt place yet?

13:45.386 --> 13:46.821
Actually, Stan,
that was a trick.

13:46.888 --> 13:48.388
We're in Philadelphia.

13:48.440 --> 13:49.523
Take a look.

13:49.574 --> 13:51.909
Does this bring
back any memories?

13:51.977 --> 13:53.978
Oh, you want me
to confront Father Roy

13:54.045 --> 13:55.379
about what happened
at camp.

13:55.447 --> 13:58.716
Thing is, I'm not sure
it was entirely his fault.

13:58.784 --> 14:00.684
I may have deserved it.

14:00.752 --> 14:02.987
In fact, I <i>may</i>
have instigated it.

14:03.054 --> 14:05.606
Actually, Francine,
I seduced <i>him.</i>

14:05.674 --> 14:08.425
<i>I don't know why I wanted him,</i>
<i>but I wanted him.</i>

14:08.510 --> 14:09.777
<i>There was no actual</i>

14:09.845 --> 14:11.011
inser...
Stan, no!

14:11.079 --> 14:12.746
This isn't about that!

14:12.814 --> 14:14.882
This wasn't
always a church.

14:14.950 --> 14:17.318
This used to be
Mr. Johnson's restaurant.

14:18.520 --> 14:20.254
Remember the dinner
you had here?

14:20.322 --> 14:22.256
Remember what
it meant to you?

14:22.324 --> 14:25.192
Don't let Roger steal
that dream from you.

14:28.613 --> 14:31.115
Clearly there's some kind
of natural gas leak.

14:31.183 --> 14:32.766
They really have
to stop building here.

14:36.538 --> 14:38.005
Ashley, come on!

14:38.073 --> 14:39.640
It was all a big
misunderstanding.

14:39.708 --> 14:40.808
Really?

14:40.876 --> 14:43.110
Well, is it a
misunderstanding

14:43.161 --> 14:44.795
that Julia's
period is late?!

14:44.863 --> 14:47.431
What?
I don't blame
Snot, okay?

14:47.499 --> 14:50.484
Julia told me <i>she</i> was
the one who jumped <i>him.</i>

14:50.552 --> 14:53.120
Great! So you and I can
pick up where we left off.

14:53.188 --> 14:56.690
Oh, I wish, but I really just
need to be with Julia right now.

14:56.758 --> 14:59.460
She decided not
to keep the baby.

14:59.528 --> 15:01.161
Oh, wow.

15:01.229 --> 15:02.730
Well, uh, Snot and I

15:02.797 --> 15:04.765
are gonna give you
our complete support.

15:04.833 --> 15:07.535
Aw, I knew
you were a sweetie.

15:07.602 --> 15:11.071
And soon I'm gonna
taste that sweetness.

15:12.657 --> 15:13.958
Ah!

15:14.025 --> 15:16.026
This cold locker ought to
relieve my swelling.

15:19.097 --> 15:21.432
Qui-Lo, open the damn door!

15:25.503 --> 15:26.570
Lovers' quarrel?

15:26.638 --> 15:27.905
What the hell
are you doin?

15:27.973 --> 15:29.106
I fired you.

15:29.174 --> 15:31.041
I got a loan
from Francine's parents,

15:31.109 --> 15:32.977
and I'm opening a restaurant
next door.

15:33.044 --> 15:34.778
It's gonna kick your ass.

15:34.846 --> 15:37.414
Ha! <i>You</i> open a restaurant?

15:37.482 --> 15:39.083
You couldn't open
a French whore's legs

15:39.150 --> 15:40.351
with a wheel of cheese.

15:40.418 --> 15:42.052
Well, I've got some help.

15:42.120 --> 15:44.438
He's late 'cause
he has to quit first.

15:48.509 --> 15:49.676
Fine, quit!

15:49.728 --> 15:51.328
You're a bum, Qui-Lo!

15:51.396 --> 15:53.030
You think you can
treat people like this

15:53.098 --> 15:54.565
because you've got
everything going for you?!

15:54.633 --> 15:57.217
Well, obviously you can
because I'm fine with you,

15:57.285 --> 15:59.920
and I'll be rooting for you
in the bike race this Friday!

16:02.324 --> 16:03.924
Wow, Francine!

16:03.992 --> 16:06.026
This is exactly
what I wanted!

16:06.094 --> 16:08.062
♪ ♪

16:10.432 --> 16:12.883
And this is exactly what
I was afraid of.

16:12.951 --> 16:14.351
No one's coming.

16:14.419 --> 16:17.187
Roger was right,
my ideas <i>are</i> stupid.

16:18.423 --> 16:19.356
Stan!

16:19.424 --> 16:20.808
It's a whoopee cushion.

16:20.875 --> 16:23.043
They're on all the chairs.

16:23.111 --> 16:24.511
It's funny.

16:24.579 --> 16:26.146
Something's not right.

16:29.551 --> 16:31.118
Stan!

16:43.865 --> 16:46.817
COOKS & STAN
Welcome, chum!
You got the eats?!

16:46.885 --> 16:47.885
People love
to be greeted.

16:47.953 --> 16:48.852
We're doing that here.

16:48.920 --> 16:50.704
Right this way.

16:50.772 --> 16:51.905
Work in the area?

16:51.973 --> 16:54.625
Actually, I sing
in the D.C. Opera.

16:56.061 --> 16:57.428
Oh, excuse me!

16:57.495 --> 16:58.812
That was
a whoopee cushion.

16:58.880 --> 17:00.147
No.

17:00.215 --> 17:01.849
Here are some
chocolate chip meatballs

17:01.916 --> 17:02.967
to get you started.

17:03.034 --> 17:04.117
Ooh...!

17:05.804 --> 17:06.904
What the...?

17:06.972 --> 17:08.571
My knife went
right through my plate!

17:08.640 --> 17:09.839
Oh, th-the plate is edible.

17:09.907 --> 17:10.907
It's a pancake.

17:10.976 --> 17:12.843
A pancake plate?

17:12.911 --> 17:15.012
What a wonderful idea!

17:15.079 --> 17:16.981
♪ Pancake ♪

17:17.048 --> 17:22.453
♪ Plaaaaa...! ♪

17:22.520 --> 17:24.121
♪ ...ate! ♪

17:24.204 --> 17:25.638
Now don't let
Julia's situation

17:25.707 --> 17:27.374
put you off of sex.

17:27.442 --> 17:29.643
We should take our time
and do it safely.

17:29.711 --> 17:31.211
This bush looks great.

17:33.732 --> 17:35.199
Are you okay?

17:35.266 --> 17:37.935
Oh, Jules,
it's behind you now.

17:38.003 --> 17:41.071
Everything's
gonna be fine.

17:41.139 --> 17:42.940
What did you actually
do in there?

17:43.008 --> 17:44.074
Nothing.
I went in,

17:44.142 --> 17:45.876
gave my number
to any girl

17:45.944 --> 17:47.444
who wasn't crying,
and came back out.

17:47.512 --> 17:50.014
So, now that
everything's taken care of,

17:50.081 --> 17:51.982
you and I can get
some sex going.

17:52.050 --> 17:55.486
No. Julia's just
so emotional right now,

17:55.553 --> 17:59.089
and I just have to spend
all of my time with her.

17:59.157 --> 18:00.958
We have to get rid of that doll!

18:01.026 --> 18:03.043
No way! I'm done!

18:03.111 --> 18:04.528
Mount Vernon, dude.

18:04.612 --> 18:06.547
I hated that trip!

18:06.614 --> 18:08.866
I pooed my pants
on the bus ride there.

18:08.933 --> 18:10.934
That's a long time

18:11.002 --> 18:12.669
to pretend you don't
smell anything.

18:12.737 --> 18:14.505
Don't go in there!

18:14.589 --> 18:15.989
Come eat
at my restaurant!

18:16.057 --> 18:17.324
Hey, Roger,
ya got the eats?

18:17.392 --> 18:19.076
Sorry, Stan,
I'm a little busy right now.

18:19.144 --> 18:20.711
You know, lunch rush.

18:22.680 --> 18:24.281
Welcome. Do you
have a reservation?

18:24.349 --> 18:25.599
Uh...
No problem.

18:25.667 --> 18:27.568
Why don't you have
a drink at the bar,

18:27.635 --> 18:29.486
and we'll see if we
can find you a table.

18:30.855 --> 18:32.923
What can I get you, Mac?

18:32.991 --> 18:34.691
Uh, I'm meeting friends at...

18:34.759 --> 18:36.193
Can I use
your crapper?

18:36.261 --> 18:37.327
Get out of here!

18:37.395 --> 18:38.529
There's a bathroom
in the park!

18:38.596 --> 18:39.630
The service here sucks!

18:39.697 --> 18:41.265
Have you even
seen a waiter?

18:41.332 --> 18:43.317
What am I doing?
This isn't helping me.

18:45.587 --> 18:47.554
Macaroni and sweet tarts!

18:47.622 --> 18:49.890
WAITER & COOKS:
Macaroni and sweet tarts!
Stacks!

18:52.327 --> 18:53.844
MAN
Gah! Good God!

18:53.912 --> 18:55.546
There's a cockroach
in my salad!

18:56.581 --> 18:57.965
I'm terribly sorry!

18:58.032 --> 18:59.066
Wait a second.

18:59.134 --> 19:00.134
This is a food restaurant.

19:00.201 --> 19:01.135
We don't serve salad.

19:01.202 --> 19:03.137
Well, it came from your kitchen!

19:03.204 --> 19:05.639
Roger! Don't-don't worry,
everybody, it's fine.

19:05.707 --> 19:06.940
Don't eat here.

19:07.008 --> 19:08.475
There's a clean restaurant
next door.

19:08.543 --> 19:09.777
If that's really
from our kitchen,

19:09.844 --> 19:10.944
then you can eat the plate.

19:22.891 --> 19:24.358
Delicious.

19:24.425 --> 19:26.143
Tito, I need you
to fix the vibe.

19:26.211 --> 19:28.245
You know what to do.

19:28.313 --> 19:30.314
♪ ♪

19:35.303 --> 19:36.336
Hey, Ashley.

19:36.404 --> 19:38.305
I just came by
to check on Julia.

19:38.373 --> 19:39.840
That's so nice of you.

19:43.411 --> 19:45.312
Julia! No!

19:46.664 --> 19:49.216
Oh, look,
it's her suicide note.

19:49.284 --> 19:51.819
"Dear Ashley,
I'm in a better place.

19:51.886 --> 19:53.754
Have sex with Steve."

19:53.822 --> 19:56.089
Mmm, in loving memoriam

19:56.157 --> 19:58.358
to your best friend's
dying wish...

19:58.426 --> 19:59.793
Wait a minute.

19:59.861 --> 20:03.163
This... this is not
her handwriting.

20:03.231 --> 20:05.232
She was murdered!

20:05.300 --> 20:07.601
We <i>cannot</i> fool around

20:07.669 --> 20:09.903
while her killer is still
on the loose!

20:09.971 --> 20:11.939
Oh! that's it.
I'm out of here.

20:12.006 --> 20:14.291
Snot, it didn't work!

20:16.444 --> 20:17.861
You're a real weirdo!

20:17.929 --> 20:19.096
You know that?

20:22.450 --> 20:24.101
Well, my restaurant's
going under, Stan.

20:25.286 --> 20:26.453
You win.

20:26.521 --> 20:28.055
I acted like an ass.

20:28.122 --> 20:29.189
I'm sorry.

20:29.257 --> 20:30.757
You know,
I'm not even mad.

20:30.825 --> 20:32.576
In fact, I should
be thanking you.

20:32.644 --> 20:34.511
If you hadn't been
such a controlling jerk,

20:34.579 --> 20:36.897
I wouldn't have been mad
enough to try it on my own.

20:36.965 --> 20:38.398
Did you recapture
any of those feelings

20:38.466 --> 20:39.900
from when you were a kid

20:39.968 --> 20:40.901
in Mr. Johnson's
restaurant?

20:40.969 --> 20:41.985
You know, I did.

20:42.070 --> 20:43.604
It really felt good

20:43.655 --> 20:45.472
feeding the people
and making them smile.

20:45.523 --> 20:47.174
So, yeah, it was
pretty much the same.

20:47.242 --> 20:49.593
What do you say we make it
<i>exactly</i> the same?

20:49.661 --> 20:50.627
How do you mean?

20:51.663 --> 20:52.779
What the hell?!

20:52.830 --> 20:54.414
I was in over my head
financially.

20:54.482 --> 20:55.582
But why <i>my</i> place?

20:55.650 --> 20:57.117
No one will suspect

20:57.185 --> 20:59.169
a successful restaurateur
of arson, Stan.

20:59.237 --> 21:02.289
And it's spreading
to mine...

21:02.357 --> 21:03.323
right now.

21:03.391 --> 21:04.324
Oh, yeah!

21:04.392 --> 21:05.626
I'm gonna kill you!

21:05.677 --> 21:07.044
Whoa! Whoa-whoa-whoa,
take it easy.

21:07.128 --> 21:09.046
You just, you just need
to calm down, okay?

21:09.130 --> 21:10.130
Yeah, okay.

21:10.181 --> 21:12.049
Just relax.

